# =============================================================================
# CATATAN PENTING
# =============================================================================
#
# File yang SENGAJA di-commit (tidak di-ignore):
#   ✅ pubspec.yaml          — dependency declarations
#   ✅ pubspec.lock          — reproducible builds (untuk app, bukan library)
#   ✅ analysis_options.yaml — lint rules
#   ✅ .gitignore            — file ini sendiri
#   ✅ lib/core/constants/amalan_data.dart  — master data amalan (hardcoded)
#   ✅ assets/               — semua asset (Lottie JSON, SVG, font)
#   ✅ test/                 — semua file unit test
#
# File yang JANGAN PERNAH di-commit:
#   ❌ *.jks / *.keystore    — Android signing key
#   ❌ *.p12 / *.p8          — iOS signing certificate
#   ❌ google-services.json  — Firebase config
#   ❌ .env / secrets.dart   — API keys & secrets
#   ❌ *.hive                — Data lokal user
#
# =============================================================================
